snippet.title: Fibbage 4 Is Available Now in The Jackbox Party Pack 9!
snippet.description:
The Jackbox Party Pack 9 is available now on Steam, Nintendo Switch, Xbox, PlayStation, Amazon Luna, Apple TV/iPad, and more. 

Save your next party with friends or family! Play five uproarious new games in one Party Pack: the trivia bluff-off Fibbage 4, the team sorting test Quixort, the magical joke auction Junktopia, the silly guessfest Nonsensory and the salacious reality TV game Roomerang.

Learn more at https://www.jackboxgames.com/fibbage-four/
